# =====================================
# 1. 建置與編譯輸出 (Build & Output)
# =====================================
**/target/
**/build/
**/*.class
/dist/
frontend/dist/
# 避免誤殺原始碼目錄下的同名資料夾
!**/src/main/**/target/
!**/src/test/**/target/
!**/src/main/**/build/
!**/src/test/**/build/
# =====================================
# 2. 系統與開發工具暫存 (OS & IDE)
# =====================================
# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.log
# IntelliJ IDEA / NetBeans / Eclipse
**/.idea/
**/*.iml
**/*.ipr
**/*.iws
/nbproject/private/
/nbbuild/
/nbdist/
/.nb-gradle/
**/.metadata/
**/.recommenders/
**/.settings/
**/.classpath
**/.project
**/.factorypath
**/.apt_generated
**/.springBeans
**/.sts4-cache
# VS Code 
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
*.code-workspace
# =====================================
# 3. 前端暫存 (Frontend - Vue / Node)
# =====================================
node_modules/
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*
**/coverage/
**/.eslintcache
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
# =====================================
# 4. 後端暫存與敏感配置 (Backend - Spring Boot)
# =====================================
HELP.md
**/HELP.md
.mvn/wrapper/maven-wrapper.jar
**/application.yaml

# 忽略根目錄可能產生的特定副檔名，但必須排除 Maven 設定檔
*.pdf
*.txt
*.jar
*.xml
!pom.xml
!backend/pom.xml
!**/pom.xml
